---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Personalización de Autor | Casa L&G">
  <main class="bg-[#0b0707] text-white min-h-screen">
    
    <section class="relative min-h-[80vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden px-6 pt-24">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
         <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/60 via-transparent to-[#0b0707] z-10"></div>
         <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-[#C5A059] opacity-[0.03] blur-[150px] rounded-full"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="relative z-20 text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <p class="font-sans text-[#C5A059] tracking-[0.7em] text-[10px] md:text-[12px] uppercase mb-6 animate-slide-up">
            Usted lo imagina, Nosotros lo forjamos
        </p>
        <h1 class="font-premium text-5xl md:text-8xl text-white mb-8 tracking-tighter leading-none animate-fade-in opacity-0 [animation-fill-mode:forwards] [animation-delay:200ms]">
          PIEZAS DE <br/>
          <span class="italic text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-[#C5A059] to-white">
            Autor Único
          </span>
        </h1>
        <p class="font-sans text-white/50 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 font-light animate-fade-in opacity-0 [animation-fill-mode:forwards] [animation-delay:400ms]">
          Transforme un detalle en un legado. Seleccione cada elemento de su obsequio bajo la guía de nuestros expertos artesanos.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-10">
        
        <div class="group relative bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5 p-12 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:border-[#C5A059]/40 hover:bg-white/[0.03]">
          <span class="text-[#C5A059]/30 font-premium text-5xl absolute top-6 right-8 group-hover:text-[#C5A059] transition-colors">01</span>
          <div class="mb-6 text-[#C5A059]"><i class="fa-solid fa-palette text-3xl"></i></div>
          <h3 class="font-premium text-2xl mb-4 text-white">Colores & Temática</h3>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Defina la paleta cromática y el concepto visual que mejor represente su intención o la personalidad del agasajado.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group relative bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5 p-12 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:border-[#C5A059]/40 hover:bg-white/[0.03]">
          <span class="text-[#C5A059]/30 font-premium text-5xl absolute top-6 right-8 group-hover:text-[#C5A059] transition-colors">02</span>
          <div class="mb-6 text-[#C5A059]"><i class="fa-solid fa-pen-nib text-3xl"></i></div>
          <h3 class="font-premium text-2xl mb-4 text-white">Mensajes Eternos</h3>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Caligrafía artística o grabados de precisión. Sus palabras, inmortales en el material más fino.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group relative bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5 p-12 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:border-[#C5A059]/40 hover:bg-white/[0.03]">
          <span class="text-[#C5A059]/30 font-premium text-5xl absolute top-6 right-8 group-hover:text-[#C5A059] transition-colors">03</span>
          <div class="mb-6 text-[#C5A059]"><i class="fa-solid fa-box-open text-3xl"></i></div>
          <h3 class="font-premium text-2xl mb-4 text-white">Caja de Autor</h3>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Diseñamos el empaque desde cero: estructuras especiales, forros de seda o maderas exóticas.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group relative bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5 p-12 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:border-[#C5A059]/40 hover:bg-white/[0.03]">
          <span class="text-[#C5A059]/30 font-premium text-5xl absolute top-6 right-8 group-hover:text-[#C5A059] transition-colors">04</span>
          <div class="mb-6 text-[#C5A059]"><i class="fa-solid fa-list-check text-3xl"></i></div>
          <h3 class="font-premium text-2xl mb-4 text-white">Selección Curada</h3>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Elija entre nuestra reserva exclusiva de productos para armar una combinación armoniosa y única.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group relative bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5 p-12 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:border-[#C5A059]/40 hover:bg-white/[0.03]">
          <span class="text-[#C5A059]/30 font-premium text-5xl absolute top-6 right-8 group-hover:text-[#C5A059] transition-colors">05</span>
          <div class="mb-6 text-[#C5A059]"><i class="fa-solid fa-building-shield text-3xl"></i></div>
          <h3 class="font-premium text-2xl mb-4 text-white">Branding de Élite</h3>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Personalización corporativa de alta fidelidad que respeta y eleva la identidad de su institución.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group relative bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5 p-12 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:border-[#C5A059]/40 hover:bg-white/[0.03]">
          <span class="text-[#C5A059]/30 font-premium text-5xl absolute top-6 right-8 group-hover:text-[#C5A059] transition-colors">06</span>
          <div class="mb-6 text-[#C5A059]"><i class="fa-solid fa-crown text-3xl"></i></div>
          <h3 class="font-premium text-2xl mb-4 text-white">Ediciones de Reserva</h3>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Acceso a materiales y productos de edición limitada disponibles solo para proyectos de co-creación.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 text-center px-6">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto border-t border-white/10 pt-16">
        <h2 class="font-premium text-3xl md:text-5xl mb-8">¿Damos vida a su idea?</h2>
        <p class="text-white/50 mb-12 font-sans tracking-wide">Inicie una consulta privada con nuestro diseñador senior para su proyecto especial.</p>
        <a href="https://wa.me/51953435738" target="_blank" class="inline-block px-14 py-5 bg-white text-black font-sans font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] transition-all hover:bg-[#C5A059] hover:text-white shadow-2xl">
          Comenzar Mi Creación
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  @keyframes slide-up {
    from { transform: translateY(40px); opacity: 0; }
    to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
  }
  @keyframes fade-in {
    from { opacity: 0; }
    to { opacity: 1; }
  }
  .animate-slide-up { animation: slide-up 1.2s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1); }
  .animate-fade-in { animation: fade-in 1.8s ease-out forwards; }
  .font-premium { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; }
</style>